Name: Frostwork Cake
Desc: Increases all team members' ATK by 10% and Crit. DMG by 16%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
Bg:
Snacks kept by Youhu in her ice cauldron, always cool to the touch. 
Itâ€™s difficult for Youhu to find food and accommodations while she travels around Solaris hunting for antiquities. These tasty cakes are what keep her from starving at times like these.
Youhu likes to put fruits in the cauldron too. As a result, the moist crusts of the cakes always gives off the faint fragrance of the seasonal fruits.
